title: Grades logical or not?
body:
https://gyazo.com/d0a99e328ab7f45c97831aa9cfc3dca8

Look at Taliyah and look at Gragas.

Gragas got an S+.
Taliyah got an S. 

Taliyah had better stats all around and more gold, but literally 7 less farm. 
LOL

Other stats:
More dmg to champions was Taliyah (highest in game actually)
Higher vision score

HOWEVER -- Gragas had 4 turret last hits and Taliyah had 1

:O 

Whatchyu guys think?
